import Button from 'react-bootstrap/Button';
import Container from 'react-bootstrap/Container';
import Nav from 'react-bootstrap/Nav';
import Navbar from 'react-bootstrap/Navbar';
import Offcanvas from 'react-bootstrap/Offcanvas';

function OffcanvasExample() {
  return (
    <>
      {['sm'].map((expand) => (
        <Navbar key={expand}  expand={expand}>
          <Container fluid>
            <Navbar.Brand ></Navbar.Brand>
            <Navbar.Toggle aria-controls={`offcanvasNavbar-expand-${expand}`} />
            <Navbar.Offcanvas 
        style={{backgroundColor:'#f7ac99'}}
              id={`offcanvasNavbar-expand-${expand}`}
              aria-labelledby={`offcanvasNavbarLabel-expand-${expand}`}
              placement="top"
              className='h-100 text-center'
            >
              <Offcanvas.Header closeButton >
                <Offcanvas.Title id={`offcanvasNavbarLabel-expand-${expand}`}></Offcanvas.Title>
              </Offcanvas.Header>
              <Offcanvas.Body >
              <Nav className="ms-auto fw-bold mt-2 ">
                  <Nav.Link className="mx-2 " href="/Shop">
                    Shop
                  </Nav.Link>
                  <Nav.Link className="mx-2" href="/commission">
                    Commissions
                  </Nav.Link>
                  <Nav.Link className="mx-2" href="/delivery">
                    Delivery
                  </Nav.Link>
                  <Nav.Link className="mx-2" href="/About">
                    About
                  </Nav.Link>
                  <Nav.Link className="mx-2" href="/Contacts">
                    Contacts
                  </Nav.Link>
                </Nav>
                <Nav className="ms-5  fw-bold ">
                  <Nav.Link className="mx-4 " href="/guide">
                    <Button
                      style={{
                        backgroundColor: "#ffcc00",
                        border: "none",
                        borderRadius: "0rem",
                        width: "8.5rem",
                        height: "2.5rem",
                        fontSize: "0.91em",
                      }}
                      className="fw-bold text-white"
                    >
                      Buy e-guide
                    </Button>
                  </Nav.Link>
                  <Nav.Link className="ms-2 mt-2" href="/english">
                    English
                  </Nav.Link>
                  <Nav.Link className="me-1 mt-2" href="/pyccknn">
                    Русский
                  </Nav.Link>
                </Nav>
                
                
              </Offcanvas.Body>
            </Navbar.Offcanvas>
          </Container>
        </Navbar>
      ))}
    </>
  );
}

export default OffcanvasExample;
